Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.25,0:00:31.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那麼今年也  拍一張背著書包的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:34.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,然後小心翼翼地收起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.09,0:00:37.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,裝滿了
