Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:22.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是他人  對我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:27.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真可愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.22,0:03:31.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您今天心情不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:33.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:36.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,購買不是義務而是權利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:39.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是漫畫不是讓讀者想著「買」
