Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:45.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:48.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是溫柔的世界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:50.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,開  開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:53.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這種像神一樣的讀者怎麼可能存在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:54.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:59.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,想要讓讀者也成為溫柔世界的居民的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:04.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我們創作方得率先成為溫柔世界的居民才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:07.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我擦我擦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:10.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我有幸能使用著橡皮擦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:12.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我網我網
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:17.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我有幸能畫著麻煩的網格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:21.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我有幸能畫著複雜的俯角街道背景
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.44,0:04:25.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如何  成為溫柔世界的居民後的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:28.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,非常清爽的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:31.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為啥感覺社畜感這麼重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:36.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是的  我們有幸能登上主流周刊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:38.79,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:37.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有幸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:43.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是的是的  老實說本想讓他再加把勁的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:46.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,難得讓他登上主流周刊了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:52.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就是你嗎  溫柔世界的破壞者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:53.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,突然怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:56.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你就沒有對他人的感激之情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:00.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,當然有的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:03.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,特別是對全國的書店
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:06.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我都抱著一腔感謝他們讓我們發售的感激之情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:10.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這確實很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:11.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是的  所以呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:14.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:17.33,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：源自三洋堂  Animate  有隣堂  喜久屋書店  虎穴  Melonbooks
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:17.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不同書店特典插畫卡片二十張
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:19.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,二十…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:26.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,身為溫柔世界的居民真是辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:30.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,最近我家小孩完全不聽我話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:31.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我家也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:35.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,明明小孩只要聽家長的話就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:38.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也不想想是誰在辛苦養育他們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:41.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.77,0:05:47.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,至少我是  有幸能夠撫養孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:48.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:53.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:58.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,工作真開心  工作真開心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:06:06.46,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}工作真開心  工作真開心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:01.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那是怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:06.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,溫柔世界的居民接了太多的工作快要爆炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:08.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這幾天…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:17.48,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\c&H585664&\pos(1364.8,433.2)}贈品用色紙10張（彩色）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:11.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好的  當然了  請讓我畫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:17.48,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\c&H515160&\pos(688,433.6)}尻名老師fanbook  商稿4格8頁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:17.48,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：源自久米田康治的好友椎名高志
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:14.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好的  當然了  請讓我畫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:17.48,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\c&H545161&\pos(225.2,431.2)}動畫的ed卡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:17.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好的  當然了  請讓我畫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:19.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這日程表是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:22.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,接到工作  不是件很值得感激的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:25.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師變了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:28.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真的  這都成社畜了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:30.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不  漫畫家都是個體戶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:34.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也就是說現在的老師不是社畜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:35.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而是漫畜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:44.25,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}是漫畜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:40.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這個創造了新的詞語後滿足的樣子是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:44.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,該說是釀成了成就感還是興奮感總之快停下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:47.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這是漫畫家最近在畫漫畫以外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:49.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也得做各種各樣的事情的一個時代
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:52.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,漫畜化的進展越來越深了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:53.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,比如這個簽售會什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:55.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,簽售會？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:57.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,誰的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:06:58.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,誰的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:00.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:03.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在混亂之中接下了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:04.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你這漫畜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:06.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,漫畜就是您自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:08.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在人們面前露臉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:09.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是被姬發現了該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:11.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,得趕快拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:13.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要取消已經不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:15.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在網上都發過公告了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:20.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而且還是星期天  這天要和姬一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:22.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我很期待星期天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:26.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,終於預約到KidZanira了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:29.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,KidZanira？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:31.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是在小孩裡很有人氣的主題公園
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:31.80,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：源自Kidzania家庭教育娛樂中心遊樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:36.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,能體驗各種職業  要預約到也很難哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:38.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.60,0:07:39.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:45.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可是  為什麼老師他突然就變為那樣的好人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:47.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,難道發生過什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:49.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,肯定是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:58.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,差不多也該停止送書包了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:03.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,讓我每年該怎麼說明才好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:06.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還是懷恨在心麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:10.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說沒有懷恨在心也是騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:13.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你也成為家長了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:16.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也稍微體會到一些我這邊的心情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:23.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如果在將來  姬帶回來的結婚對象
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:26.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是個在畫名叫「雞雞復雞雞」漫畫的男人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:29.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你能允許麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.52,0:08:31.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能會允許
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:34.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:35.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,再會了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:43.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,確實…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:46.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我絕不可能把姬託付給
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:47.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在畫我這種漫畫的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:51.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,絕對不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:52.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,自我矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:58.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在畫「雞雞復雞雞」這種漫畫的傢伙簽名啥的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:08:59.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有誰會想要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:04.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然發生了什麼導致失去自信了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.93,0:09:08.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好人化是喪失自信的負面表現麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:10.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,反正簽售會誰都不會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:11.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我要陪姬去玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:13.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這可不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:20.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這說不定  兩邊都可以兼顧哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:28.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,再往前面大人不可進入了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:30.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:32.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,玩開心點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:38.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原來如此  這麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:39.72,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,0)\bord0\pos(787.2,300.8)\c&HFFFFFF&}幾天前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:43.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼才能同時兼顧KidZanira和簽售會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:47.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在KidZanira基本上大人都只是在等候室裡看著孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:51.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在這期間舉行簽售會就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.73,0:09:55.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,看  簽售會會場的書店在同一棟建築裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:58.57,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：書店名源自紀伊國屋書店
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:57.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,超幸運的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:09:58.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:00.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我說這也太近了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:03.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是發生點什麼情況偶遇了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:05.20,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&HB8A6C7&\pos(668.8,62.8)}黃段子漫畫家簽售會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:04.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:06.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不行不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:07.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:09.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是也只能硬著頭皮上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:11.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大家都會幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:14.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:15.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.38,0:10:20.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,簽名程度的話這身打扮也能畫的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:21.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:23.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,畫不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:29.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在那拐角轉過去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:33.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然我還是回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.27,0:10:34.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了啊突然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.02,0:10:36.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,反正誰都不會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:39.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,相當缺乏自信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:41.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒事的  會來很多人的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:42.37,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.2,755.2)\c&H393B48&}毫無根據
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:43.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好啦搞快點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:45.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不行不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:46.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:49.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:51.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,排成長隊了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:53.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以我都說了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:56.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,會來很多人的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:01.93,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\pos(803.6,21.2)\org(970,21.2)\frx348\fry0}路堤君  簽售會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:01.93,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fs40\pos(1150.4,260.8)\org(1270.4,257.6)\frx352\fry4}寫真集發售紀念
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:10:59.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,路堤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:04.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是當地吉祥物的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.55,0:11:05.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,簽售會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:12.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還挺難的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:17.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為什麼是我來擔任監護人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:20.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您家的孩子也在做糕點師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:25.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我只是看著小女孩  我的孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:30.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,只是看別人家的小孩  會被當作是可疑人士的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:32.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是…是女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:34.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那個齊瀏海的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:37.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,今天是爸爸一個人來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:40.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我想想  母親因為工作關係…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:43.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,星期天工作什麼的真是辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:44.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,妻子她…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:46.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是國際航線的空姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:48.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,現在正在飛海外的航班上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:50.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,換人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:51.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,抱歉  給你這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:56.61,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\pos(286,138)\c&H42464F&}丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:56.61,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\pos(86,650)\c&H42464F&}女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:56.61,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1222,134)\c&H42464F&}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:54.48,kakushigoto in 10 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz269.1\c&H4F5B6D&\fs75\pos(1086,412)}身高175cm
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:56.61,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1400,290)\c&H4F5B6D&}國際航班空姐（德航）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:56.61,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\fs65\c&H4F5B6D&\pos(1600,360)}IQ 200
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:53.10,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\c&H4F5B6D&\pos(1340,550)}原小平市選美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:53.10,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\c&H4F5B6D&\pos(1536,688)}托業860分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:53.10,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\c&H4F5B6D&\pos(1198,834)}武將的後裔（故意沒說是誰）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:53.10,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\c&H4F5B6D&\pos(1208,992)}cookpad上粉絲超過1萬人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:54.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:56.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬媽媽的角色設定圖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.86,0:11:59.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你這種設定漫畫裡都行不通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:01.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,哎呀  您是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:04.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,妻子現在應該在航班上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:08.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我是…那孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:09.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:13.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我15歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:18.67,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\pos(550,28)\c&H585C5E&}「風之緊身褲」後藤可久士老師簽售會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:18.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:19.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一個人都沒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:23.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那現在離開場還有一小時當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:27.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而且參加者都是提前抽籤中抽出的限定100位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:31.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這種手段就是讓別人覺得我是人氣作家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:33.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,然後將名額私下轉賣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:36.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,肯定是你們知道我沒什麼人氣但又不好開口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.27,0:12:38.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我知道您現在很焦慮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.19,0:12:40.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但其實最焦慮的是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:43.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,書店的工作人員們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:45.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:47.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,書店的工作人員們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:49.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他們可是拚盡了全力不讓作家蒙羞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:52.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,甚至是到了危急時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:54.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他們可以換成便裝然後來排隊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.41,0:12:55.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我就知道是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.58,0:12:59.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你們的臉我記住了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:02.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如果讓我看到你們在排隊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:03.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我就哭給你們看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:06.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,看來又來了一位讓人頭疼的作家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:20.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,能夠體驗這麼多職業啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.02,0:13:23.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,請容許我再提醒一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:25.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,簽售會是一場和時間賽跑的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:27.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如果您要畫角色的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:29.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,每個人畫一個就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:31.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還有  為了防止簽名轉賣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:33.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,請一定要寫上粉絲名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.45,0:13:36.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那麼我們就開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:39.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,排隊的托兒準備好了就請開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.29,0:13:43.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,請各位粉絲進場
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:45.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,麻煩您了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:48.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我是老師您的忠實粉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:51.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這哪是托兒啊  完全就是自己人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:55.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真就除了這麼明顯的托兒以外就找不到人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:58.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我可是正經地參加了抽籤然後被選中的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:13:59.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,請您簽名
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:02.52,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}致一子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:02.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:04.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太謝謝您了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:07.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,麻煩您了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:09.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好像沒見過這人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:11.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可能是真正的粉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:14.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小桃  你來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:17.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我被選中了  真是太幸運了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:19.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你要是給我說一聲  我就去拜託老師給你一張簽名的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:21.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那樣也太不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:23.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,給您
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:25.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太謝謝您了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:27.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,剛才那女生  是我的大學朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.01,0:14:29.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,她好久以前就是老師的忠實粉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:31.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你以為我會信？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:32.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:34.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是太慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:36.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,像這樣的關懷方式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:38.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,明明對誰都沒有好處
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:40.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可是這群傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.35,0:14:43.86,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}呵呵  呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:43.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他們被強迫參與排隊  為什麼看上去還這麼高興
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:45.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我知道了  這群傢伙是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:47.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您是打工的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:50.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您居然知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.74,0:14:51.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我的確是個打工的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:52.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:53.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,深夜的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:56.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我一邊在便利店打工一邊朝著成為漫畫家努力著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:57.12,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,818)\c&H4A4447&}沒在聽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:14:59.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,麻煩您了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.08,0:15:01.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您也是打工的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:02.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是  我是臨時工
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.33,0:15:06.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,居然明顯到了直接說自己是臨時工的這種地步
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:08.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,總是升不到正式員工
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:09.01,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\c&H4A4447&\pos(430,786)}沒在聽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:11.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您的時薪是多少
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:16.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我住在鄉下  時薪大概是850日元左右
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:19.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是他們會為我報銷路費
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:21.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:24.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師  上午的50名已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:26.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您休息一會兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:28.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我說  十丸院
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:31.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你再給他們漲點時薪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:36.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我和姬約好了一起吃午飯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:42.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這是我在店裡做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:44.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,看上去玩得很開心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:47.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我可是嚴格把控品質了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.92,0:15:49.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,除此之外還體驗了什麼工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:53.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,糕點師  快遞員
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:54.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還有警察
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:58.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我好想一直這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:01.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師  快到下午的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:03.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,趕快點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:06.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師  您在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:07.94,kakushigoto in 8,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\c&H2C3842&\3c&HD7E6E9&\pos(704,16)}戒潟魁吏的世界展
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:10.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我聽說這次在畫展在上野舉辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:11.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:14.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這人可是日本畫界的大家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:18.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我超級喜歡這人的畫  很敬仰他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:22.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,居然是這麼厲害的一個人物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:26.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我家裡有一幅  下次要不給你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.83,0:16:28.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師您又在開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:31.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,繪畫大師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:33.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,同是畫畫的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:35.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,和畫連環畫的我相比
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:36.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是雲泥之別啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:40.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太慢了  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:42.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還要繼續嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:44.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這種事情對誰都沒好處
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:47.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我明白老師您剛才說的意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:50.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他們怎麼可能是來打工的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:52.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你有證據嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:55.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就老師您簽售會掙來的那點錢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:57.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還不夠支付託兒們的工資呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:00.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,「就」是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:04.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真不知道您的職業尊嚴到底還在不在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:06.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師您看看這些
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:08.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,都是粉絲送來的信和禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:11.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您覺得打工的可能做到這個地步嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:15.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他們可是真的喜歡老師您的漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:17.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您稍微對自己有些自信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.09,0:17:19.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,下午的簽售會開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:25.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:27.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,雖然我還是有些難以相信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.81,0:17:30.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這群人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.77,0:17:32.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,全都…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:39.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,讀過我的漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.08,0:17:42.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但這還不能夠告訴姬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:44.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,拜託您了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.21,0:17:50.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,看起來您是帶著小孩子來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:52.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他知道我畫的是什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.92,0:17:54.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我畫的可是黃色段子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.46,0:17:56.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他當然知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:17:58.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我們父子倆都是您的粉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.76,0:18:05.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  緊身褲誒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:06.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:08.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}你可要好好保管它哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:08.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:12.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以我才叫您稍微對自己有些信心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:15.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您看  就連那麼小的孩子也是您的粉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:19.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真的是  就連那麼小的孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:22.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是僱傭了  可就是違反法律了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:23.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你指這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:25.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:28.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我只是為我相信的漫畫而畫而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:30.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:33.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他好像重新拾起信心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.50,0:18:37.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,無論繪畫大師怎麼對我說三道四
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:40.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我的職業就是漫畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.48,0:18:54.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,被…被發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:18:59.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,趕快換人  輪到我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:03.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師  您在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:06.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我在體…體驗工作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:09.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原來這裡是大人們的Kidzanira
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:11.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:14.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,畢竟大人們在等待的時候很無聊嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:21.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我還得去找爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:25.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸到了約好的時間還沒來  一定是迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:29.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是和家裡的打扮出入太大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:32.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以沒能認出您來是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:35.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您的漫畫家COSPLAY第一次立功了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.11,0:19:37.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這才不是COSPLAY
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:42.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,今天什麼工作比較開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:45.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,全部都很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:50.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但最開心的還是當書店員工
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.67,0:19:55.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是  很辛苦的工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:56.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但我真的很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:00.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸給你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:01.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這是送給你的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.13,0:20:04.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你是從哪裡得來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:06.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我工作買來的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:09.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,工作？在Kidzanira工作得來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:13.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,工作的話就能得到一種叫Kidz的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:16.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在那裡就可以使用它購買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:19.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬工作為我買來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:23.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:27.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但那個的門票一定很貴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:31.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,畢竟是花了錢才讓我工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:35.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,本來畫畫這工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:39.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,即使讓我付錢我也願意做下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:40.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.21,0:20:45.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我還能將這份工作做到多久
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:51.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那個  大人版的Kidzanira也有工作介紹處嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:55.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  你有去過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:21:00.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,以後我可能會去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:08.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那裡有著箱子的後續
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:12.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那些箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.62,0:21:17.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是爸爸為我準備的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:22.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,漫畫？
