Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.59,0:21:25.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那是一本
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:28.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,特別特別無趣的漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.26,0:21:31.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒有劍也沒有魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:34.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒有任何的波瀾起伏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.85,0:21:36.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,只有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.06,0:21:39.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  媽媽  和女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.02,0:21:44.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一家三口平凡的生活故事
