Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.95,0:21:51.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但這無趣的日常生活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.74,0:21:56.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,才是最為夢幻的故事
